parts.text:
<OUTPUT_JSON>[
  {
    "action_type": "TYPE",
    "selector": "input[name*=account i]",
    "text": "[Account Information]",
    "description": "Enter the relevant account identifier (e.g., patient ID, case number, library item code) for the record being maintained."
  },
  {
    "action_type": "TYPE",
    "selector": "input[name*=amount i], input[type=number]",
    "text": "[Numerical Data]",
    "description": "Enter any associated numerical data (e.g., billing amount, quantity, reference number, item count) for the record."
  },
  {
    "action_type": "TYPE",
    "selector": "textarea[name*=memo i]",
    "text": "[Detailed Memo or Notes]",
    "description": "Input detailed notes, summary, observations, or any relevant textual information for the medical record, library item, or correspondence."
  },
  {
    "action_type": "CLICK",
    "selector": "button:has-text(\"post\" i), button:has-text(\"save\" i)",
    "description": "Click to save or post the entered/updated information, thereby maintaining the record."
  }
]</OUTPUT_JSON>
